{"tid":566544,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"義工年初一送草給創興牛牛　被漁護署指控「亂拋垃圾」","createTime":"2018-02-20T04:42:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-21T03:57:51.000Z","uid":48083,"like":140,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":70,"replies":[{"pid":"371bca98b9299ef58e551fe5c14a1fdc22fc6eba","tid":566544,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T04:42:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/cccc_9JLQr_1200x0.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fcccc_9JLQr_1200x0.PNG&h=01f4904e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖為年初二時，牛義工再帶草給牛牛。<br />\n<br />\n一班牛義工在大年初一早上帶草到創興的牛賀新年，想不到竟遇到一班部署好的漁護署職員，當義工們放下草後，他們即上前拍攝，及要求義工交出身份證，指控他們「亂拋垃圾」。義工不服，他們與漁護署職員都即場報警，結果警員到場後仍命令義工交出身份證。一名當天沒到場的義工對本報稱，漁護署的做法令人憤怒，「我們自費買草給牛吃，怎會是垃圾？」<br />\n<br />\n這班牛義工在前年得悉有些西貢牛被遷往創興後，擔心那些草不適合牛吃，便開始自費買草給那裡的牛吃。義工們初一早上9時帶草到創興，想不到早已有漁護署職員準備，一見他們放低草便上前拍攝，又帶走部分草聲稱要化驗，更指控義工亂拋垃圾。<br />\n<br />\n有義工指，這已不是第一次被漁護署針對，去年11月有班義工也被漁護署指控亂拋垃圾，惟未知會否收到告票。<br />\n<br />\n漁護署近年多次將一些受傷醫好的牛，遷到創興這郊野公園空地，當中包括牛B，惟有部分牛義工擔心該處沒有足夠高的草供牛食用，而政府則強調牛會有方法在附近找食物，不會有食物不足的問題。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n原刊於香港動物報<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E7%BE%A9%E5%B7%A5%E5%B9%B4%E5%88%9D%E4%B8%80%E9%80%81%E8%8D%89%E7%B5%A6%E5%89%B5%E8%88%88%E7%89%9B%E7%89%9B-%E8%A2%AB%E6%BC%81%E8%AD%B7%E7%BD%B2%E6%8C%87%E6%8E%A7-%E4%BA%82%E6%8B%8B%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E7%25BE%25A9%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2588%259D%25E4%25B8%2580%25E9%2580%2581%25E8%258D%2589%25E7%25B5%25A6%25E5%2589%25B5%25E8%2588%2588%25E7%2589%259B%25E7%2589%259B-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%25BC%2581%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%258E%25A7-%25E4%25BA%2582%25E6%258B%258B%25E5%259E%2583%25E5%259C%25BE%2F&d=ERncOCiFAIM0cKEgYWaHRJ7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=3747a3a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E7%25BE%25A9%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2588%259D%25E4%25B8%2580%25E9%2580%2581%25E8%258D%2589%25E7%25B5%25A6%25E5%2589%25B5%25E8%2588%2588%25E7%2589%259B%25E7%2589%259B-%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%25BC%2581%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E7%25BD%25B2%25E6%258C%2587%25E6%258E%25A7-%25E4%25BA%2582%25E6%258B%258B%25E5%259E%2583%25E5%259C%25BE%2F&h=e90ff4b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E7%BE%A9%E5%B7%A5%E5%B9%B4%E5%88%9D%E4%B8%80%E9%80%81%E8%8D%89%E7%B5%A6%E5%89%B5%E8%88%88%E7%89%9B%E7%89%9B-%E8%A2%AB%E6%BC%81%E8%AD%B7%E7%BD%B2%E6%8C%87%E6%8E%A7-%E4%BA%82%E6%8B%8B%E5%9E%83%E5%9C%BE/</a>"},{"pid":"23b1a052d88fd665b01111b2fa2385d52735872c","tid":566544,"uid":5843,"like":423,"dislike":6,"score":417,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T04:44:24.000Z","msg":"中環南亞人唔捉<br />\n捉呢啲義工<br />\n港共政府我屌你老母"},{"pid":"98443c29d05530e5dba49f7d8a64c517c49224c8","tid":566544,"uid":63670,"like":80,"dislike":2,"score":78,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T04:45:16.000Z","msg":"繼食環狗之後<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n漁護又....."},{"pid":"5ddf6afcf8aa4eca667e3a0bab1c6d0a722ee29a","tid":566544,"uid":37869,"like":25,"dislike":3,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T04:46:16.000Z","msg":"其實咁喂佢地係咪好事"},{"pid":"554bf27560d70354456115c1147cf77c785f7253","tid":566544,"uid":63909,"like":95,"dislike":1,"score":94,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T04:48:16.000Z","msg":"大年初一早上遇到一班部署好的漁護署職員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁撚勤力裝9你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/offtopic.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a98b21772872a45cca84327b015b77e93ad2f1be","tid":566544,"uid":33808,"like":98,"dislike":4,"score":94,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T04:49:39.000Z","msg":"仲有冇人性架？<br />\n你擺明要佢自己餓死<br />\n或者永遠唔夠食嘅情況下生存<br />\n你唔鳩人道，算<br />\n政府相關機構「共性」特別高<br />\n我去比草，你又唔比<br />\n仲要借啲二控呢控路<br />\n做人使唔使做到咁賤啊？<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">會係附近搵食不成問題<br />\n咪姐係去垃圾桶嗰啲地方咯<br />\n唔係食死佢就係煩死啲工人<br />\n你老母決策嗰個就拎高薪</span>"},{"pid":"3cd60ba8141fcfa58903d5db1dfd1745ccba82ae","tid":566544,"uid":113000,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"quote":{"pid":"5ddf6afcf8aa4eca667e3a0bab1c6d0a722ee29a","tid":566544,"uid":37869,"like":25,"dislike":3,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T04:46:16.000Z","msg":"其實咁喂佢地係咪好事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T04:49:52.000Z","msg":"本身西貢牛就係無啖好食<br />\n連生肉都食問題已經存在左好多年"},{"pid":"01c7c3529351e19b451c958ac2af6bae23ab6adc","tid":566544,"uid":92064,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T04:51:31.000Z","msg":"餵得幾耐，要死點都會死"},{"pid":"92a69c3597b7fa71ed30437b7519d31191fb8ae7","tid":566544,"uid":28279,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T04:53:24.000Z","msg":"啲牛人道毀滅算，應該死硬，政府本來就係想搞掂佢哋"},{"pid":"ecbbfe8bd09b1f3f54623dfecca248ab5c78d5b3","tid":566544,"uid":64131,"like":9,"dislike":37,"score":-28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T04:54:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>餵得幾耐，要死點都會死</blockquote><br />\n咪係  唔通佢地會日日送草咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n做呢啲野滿足自己道德需要ja ma<br />\n好撚虛偽"},{"pid":"33a0e51363523ccd219deb369e517ca171e29ee4","tid":566544,"uid":37869,"like":3,"dislike":14,"score":-11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T04:55:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實咁喂佢地係咪好事</blockquote>本身西貢牛就係無啖好食<br />\n連生肉都食問題已經存在左好多年</blockquote><br />\n但係唔夠野食係大自然一向都有的問題<br />\n糧食唔夠 動物的數量自然會減少<br />\n相反 如果佢地有無限的糧食又冇天敵<br />\n數量只會不斷增加<br />\n雖然呢個係人類造成的問題<br />\n但人類應唔應該比野佢地食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺得絕育同埋養到佢地死就最好"},{"pid":"d3a7347fe62c5158b28584dd11e85049505d863f","tid":566544,"uid":3936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"554bf27560d70354456115c1147cf77c785f7253","tid":566544,"uid":63909,"like":95,"dislike":1,"score":94,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T04:48:16.000Z","msg":"大年初一早上遇到一班部署好的漁護署職員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁撚勤力裝9你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/offtopic.png\" class=\"